# Day 1 â€“ Basic Networking Lab

# Objective
Learn basics of Packet Tracer and create a simple network between two LANs using router, switches, PCs, and a server.

# Topology

Router: 2
Switches: 2
PCs: 2
Server: 2
Firewall: 2

# Steps

Added router, switches, PCs, Firewall, and server in Packet Tracer.
Connected devices using copper straight-through cables.
Set default gateways on PCs and Server.
Verified connectivity with ping.

# Result

LAN1 and LAN2 communicated successfully via the router.
